    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock. Recent mechanical stewardship includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings, maintaining the chassis's legendary communicative feedback. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its well-maintained status, the powertrain exhibits linear power delivery and the signature metallic rasp up to its 8,000 RPM redline. A mechanically robust specimen ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
