      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a reliable, stylish daily driver. The exterior retains a deep luster, though minor road-wear consistent with careful use is present upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and smoke-free, with all power features, climate control, and infotainment systems functioning perfectly. Mechanically, it is sound; the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and it has a documented history of on-time servicing. It sits on a set of premium tires with plenty of tread remaining. A complete set of owner\u2019s manuals and both original key fobs are included. This is a balanced choice for someone seeking quality and longevity without the showroom price tag.",
